import { Image, Text, View } from "react-native"

const Home = () => {
    return(
        <View>
            <View style={{alignItems:'center'}}>
                <Image style={{width:271,height:271}} source={require('../assets/Image 95.png')} />
            </View>
            <View>
                <Text style={{color:'purple'}}>
                    MANAGE YOUR TASK
                </Text>
            </View>
        </View>
    )
}
export default Home
